    "Speculating socio-ethical impacts hints at speculative design approaches which have been heavily discussed and supported by multiple studies as well (Lee et al. 2023; Alfrink et al. 2023).",
    "Analysing hypothetical situation of unpredictability to solve unpredictable behaviour of an AI system [G1], following codes of ethics and standards of practice [G18], including diverse people in the development team [G21], and having internal governance such as ethics committees in an organisation to establish AI ethical standards [G21] are also other proactive strategies we recommend.",
